name: HERMETIC SEAL OF LIGHT - GIF
description:
The 'Hermetic Seal of Light' is a symbol often referred to as the synthesis of alchemy. It hearkens back to the ancient Pythagorean philosophy. The square, circle and triangle depicted are emblems of the material body, the soul and the spirit. These were believed to be necessary for 'alchemical transformation'.

This specific design was created using pure geometry and mathematical equations. It was completed on the 3rd December 2019.
